{"id":16912,"date":"2019-04-18T06:17:22","date_gmt":"2019-04-17T23:17:22","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=16912"},"modified":"2019-11-27T22:23:05","modified_gmt":"2019-11-27T15:23:05","slug":"top-theme-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/top-theme-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging","title":{"rendered":"Top 3 theme WordPress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed k\u00e8m blogging t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm <strong>theme WordPress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<\/strong> <strong>t\u1ed1t<\/strong> v\u1eeba blogging t\u1ed1t th\u00ec h\u00e3y th\u1eed top 3 theme WordPress mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed sau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm theme WordPress cho nhu c\u1ea7u?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Blogging k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/strong> Sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n blog c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u00e1n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hay d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/li><li><strong>B\u00e1n h\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p blogging<\/strong>. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 thu nh\u1eadp ngay v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a blogging \u0111\u1ec3 SEO organic cho c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 theme sau \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Woocomerce trong tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 blog module v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p SEO structure r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Astra theme &#8211; Theme wordpress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch cao<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Astra-sites-1024x538.