a1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trang web b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 blog nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><b><a href=\"\/out\/sukipro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Suki Pro (opens in a new tab)\">Suki Pro<\/a><\/b> l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a Suki theme, t\u00ednh n\u0103ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i Astra v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t. T\u1eeb t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh Header, footer, Blocks (Custom layout \u1edf Astra), content container (h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1edbi 2 lo\u1ea1i: wide v\u00e0 narrow). M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Suki Pro c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng Vanilla code nh\u01b0 theme n\u00ean si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t (trong khi Astra pro d\u00f9ng jQuery).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i c\u0169ng chuy\u1ec3n CuongThach sang d\u00f9ng Suki theme.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xem <a href=\"https:\/\/sukiwp.com\/sites\/?ref=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo theme Suki Woocomerce \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y (opens in a new tab)\">Demo theme Suki Woocomerce \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"622\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-1024x622.png\" alt=\"Suki demo\" class=\"wp-image-17028\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-1024x622.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-218x132.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-300x182.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-700x425.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo